        </item>
        <item>
            <title>BMW X3 第四代运动型多功能 SUV 登陆香港，售价 49.9 万起 + 全新运动外形设计</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/12/bmw-x3-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bmw-x3-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/12/bmw-x3-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 03:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[bmw]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[bmw x3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286343</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>自 2003 年问世以来，BMW X3 凭借其卓越的驾驶体验，累积销量突破 370 万辆，稳固其在市场中的王者地位。经过四代车型的持续进化，BMW 于 2025 年 1 月 10 日正式于香港科学园发表全新第四代 BMW X3 运动型多功能 SUV。此次推出的 BMW X3 20 xDrive 与 BMW X3 20 xDrive M Sport Edition 两款四驱版本，展示了全新的设计语言，并由美国斯巴顿堡工厂精心制造。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286346" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112534-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112534-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112534.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>动感与现代感兼备，重新设计鬼面罩</h2><p>全新 BMW X3 的外观设计兼具力量感与动感，展现出非凡的视觉冲击力。车身长度、宽度与轴距较前代略有增加，而车身高度则稍作降低，从而塑造出更具力量感及运动感的车身线条。车头的 BMW 双肾型鬼面罩经过重新设计，细致的纹理交错融合，与 LED L 形日间行车灯、侧灯及转向指示灯一同呈现出强烈的霸气气息。选配的 BMW Iconic Glow 发光双肾型鬼面罩及动感迎宾灯进一步强化了车辆外观的现代感。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112635-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112635-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_112635.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LED L 形日间行车灯</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_114103-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_114103-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_114103.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LED L 形日间行车灯</p><p>车顶流线型设计优雅延伸至车尾，清晰锐利的车身骨线和大胆的侧裙造型，令车辆显得更具动感。车尾则配备了 T 型 LED 尾灯，并由长型车顶扰流板及侧面空气扰流器围绕，设计细节增强运动感，体现强烈的力量感。隐藏式排气尾管及突出的轮拱设计，使整体车身更显动感十足。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286355" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113154-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113154-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113154.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新设计双肾型鬼面罩</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286351" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113107-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113107-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113107.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286353" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113126-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113126-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113126.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲突出轮拱设计</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286352" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113118-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113118-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113118.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲长型车顶扰流板</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286354" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113136-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113136-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250110_113136.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲车尾则配备了 T 型 LED 尾灯</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/12/bmw-x3-2/life-tech/auto/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
